A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a futuristic assembly line in a neon-lit factory, where robotic arms with glowing cyan circuits are simultaneously constructing two distinct metallic processor chips - one sleek and angular, the other curved and organic in design. The chips float on magnetic platforms, surrounded by holographic blueprints and streaming data particles in purple and electric blue. In the background, towering server racks pulse with orange warning lights while conveyor belts carry identical container cubes into a swirling portal. The atmosphere is hazy with synthetic fog, reflecting the neon glow of the industrial space. The scene emphasizes duality and parallel creation, with mirror-image construction happening on both sides of the frame.
